docs.text: Synthesizer V Studio This website serves as an unofficial user manual for Synthesizer V Studio, since the official manual by Dreamtonics refers to the legacy version of the software from 2018. For official instructional content for SynthV Studio, check the Dreamtonics video tutorial series . Additional guides and resources can be found on synthv.info . This website is not affiliated with Dreamtonics. Report an Issue
